  "excerpt": "Today I'm back with another project in collaboration with Avery. This time I'm making an \"Oh Happy Day\" banner using their printable perforated sheets and their easy-to-use design software. Avery Design & Print Online makes it super easy to create…",
  "legacyPath": "/blog/ohhappyday",
